   107	This is a single-paragraph spec amendment, not a refactor. It
   108	preserves the v0 contract and tightens chapter 9's claim to match
   109	what the suite actually delivers.
   110	
   111	## 3. Scope
   112	
   113	### 3.1 In scope
   114	
   115	Two new chapter-9 §5 groups, with new scenario files under
